<div class="project-text">
    <h3>The Project</h3>
    <p>Another project built entirely from zero, and another one that gave real satisfaction. Nunzio, known as Killer Barman, is one of the most recognizable faces on the Italian spirits scene and genuinely one of the funniest people I have worked with. After years of developing and refining his own gins to meet very specific and demanding standards, he needed an identity to match.</p>
    <p>The goal was clean and refined without being cold, with enough personality to carry itself across physical products, the online shop and trade fair stands. It has been working well enough that there is no reason to touch it, so we are now focusing on new products and new things to make.</p>
